data.description: Spring is right around the corner and golf is right across the street. Don't miss this stunning 3 bedroom/2 bath home in White Plains! The front yard is well landscaped and gives views to Pine Hill Country Club while the back yard is fenced and cross fenced for you and your pets to enjoy. The screened back patio is the perfect place to relax and/or entertain. Inside you'll find a wide open floor plan with quality finishings and granite tops throughout. This one will be gone fast!
